---
import Mail from "./icons/general/Mail.astro";
import Location from "./icons/general/Location.astro";
---

<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-5 md:gap-6 p-4 sm:p-5 md:p-6 lg:p-8 w-full">
  <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-3 md:space-y-4">
    <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-center md:text-left">Información de Contacto</h3>
    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base lg:text-lg text-base-content/70 text-center md:text-left leading-relaxed max-w-md md:max-w-none mx-auto md:mx-0">
      ¿Tienes alguna pregunta o quieres trabajar juntos? No dudes en
      contactarme directamente.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4 md:space-y-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-base-300/20 transition-colors duration-200">
      <Mail class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base font-medium">carlony395@gmail.com</span>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-base-300/20 transition-colors duration-200">
      <Location class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 flex-shrink-0" />
      <span class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base font-medium">Cancún, México</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
